text.div:
This value set includes codes based on the following rules:

  • Import all the codes that are contained in http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/ips/ValueSet/medical-devices-uv-ips
  • Import all the codes that are contained in http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/ips/ValueSet/absent-or-unknown-devices-uv-ips

name: MedicalDevicesSnomedAbsentUnknownUvIps
title: Medical Devices - SNOMED CT + Absent/Unknown - IPS
publisher: Health Level Seven International - Patient Care Work Group
description: This value set includes codes from SNOMED Clinical Terms (SNOMED CT®) that are included in: all descendants of 49062001 \|Device (physical object)\|, plus IPS codes for absent/unknown devices.
